  }, "The \u201CAha!\u201D zones"), mdx("p", null, "Every valuable chart or pie graph has an \u201CAha!\u201D zone \u2014 a number or range of data that exhibits something essential to your point."), mdx("p", null, "Smart presenters demonstrate the significance of the \u201CAha!\u201D zone orally, sharing the learning, trend, or story the data is telling."), mdx("p", null, "Better presenters describe it out loud but also address it on the slide as a bullet."), mdx("p", null, "But the best presenters do all of the above AND visually highlight the \u201CAha!\u201D zone itself with a circle or shading to reach the differentiated (aural, verbal, visual) learners in their audience, as well as to triple-reinforce the most important data takeaways."), mdx("h2", {
